<P>
   BUTTERFLY-PRESERVE (Los Angeles) _ In the deserted dunes just
west of Los Angeles International Airport where the crumbling
foundations of homes testify to the airport's past expansions,
nature is reasserting itself in a startlingly beautiful manner. The
endangered El Segundo blue butterflies that two decades ago
