statistics show. Authorities say the prison-based Mexican Mafia,
known as La Eme, is responsible for fostering violence among gangs
by setting one against the other to collect ``drug-dealing taxes''
in the Northeast Valley. By Lisa Van Proyen. (Will move in the
``n'' California and ``a'' national news files.)
