<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-24 17:14 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2730 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-OUTDOORS-SALMON-NYT &LR;      07-24 1057
