<DOCNO> NYT19990724.0179 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-24 17:48 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2766 &Cx1f; tab-z
r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-UNBAN-TALIBAN-ECONOMI     07-24 0848
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-UNBAN-TALIBAN-ECONOMIST-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
RECOGNIZE, THEN PRESSURIZE, AFGHANISTAN'S TALIBAN GOVERNMENT  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Commentary Editors)   (This excellent 600-word ``separate buy'' article is from the
current (week beginning 24 July 1999) ECONOMIST magazine.)  
  
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
in Canada except to The Toronto Globe &AMP; Mail.)  
  
